The '''Gorodskoi Katok''' ([[Kyrgyz language|Kyrgyz]] and [[Russian language|Russian]]: Городской Каток) is an [[ice rink]] located in [[Bishkek]], [[Kyrgyzstan]]. The [[Seating capacity|capacity]] of the ice rink has 750 people. It is used for [[ice hockey]] and [[figure skating]].

