'''Salle Moulay Abdellah''' is an [[indoor arena|indoor sporting arena]] located in [[Rabat]], [[Morocco]]. The capacity of the arena is 10,000 people. The arena is used to host indoor sporting events, such as [[basketball]] and [[volleyball]].
